    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称美联储“已到或接近”放缓或暂停降息的阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/powell-says-fed-at-or-near-a-point-to-slow-pause-cuts-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，劳动力市场仍在逐渐降温，通胀仍“大致处于正轨”。鲍威尔在美联储连续第三次下调基准利率，但减少了 2025 年预期降息次数后发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/powell-says-fed-at-or-near-a-point-to-slow-pause-cuts-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 20:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新的人工智能选股者注定会令人失望：Nir Kaissar</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/new-ai-stock-pickers-destined-to-disappoint-nir-kaissar-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街对人工智能取代现实生活中的基金经理的讨论很多，大概是因为人工智能将更擅长选股。彭博社观点专栏作家 Nir ​​Kaissar 在“彭博市场”节目中告诉 Scarlet Fu，人工智能选股注定会令人失望。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/new-ai-stock-pickers-destined-to-disappoint-nir-kaissar-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 20:13:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔称通胀正接近我们的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/fed-s-powell-says-inflation-is-moving-closer-to-our-goal-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储连续第三次下调基准利率，但减少了 2025 年预期降息次数，表明态度谨慎。美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，通胀率正朝着 2% 的目标迈进。鲍威尔在华盛顿的新闻发布会上发表开场白。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/fed-s-powell-says-inflation-is-moving-closer-to-our-goal-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 20:01:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TCW 转型系统 ETF 表现优异</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/tcw-transforms-systems-etf-outperforms-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TCW 投资组合经理 Eli Horton 在《彭博市场》节目中与 Katie Greifeld 和 Scarlet Fu 谈论该公司的 Transform Systems ETF（股票代码：NETZ），该基金自 2022 年推出以来一直表现优于标准普尔 500 指数。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/tcw-transforms-systems-etf-outperforms-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 20:00:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚股市创纪录的涨势有望在 2025 年持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/australia-s-record-breaking-stocks-rally-seen-continuing-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于央行宽松政策的可能性提振市场人气，且中国的刺激计划承诺为矿业股提供支持，澳大利亚股市有望在 2025 年再次表现强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/australia-s-record-breaking-stocks-rally-seen-continuing-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金融状况并不紧张，但美联储仍在降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-12-18/financial-conditions-aren-t-tight-but-the-fed-is-still-cutting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着时间的推移，美国资产市场非理性繁荣的证据似乎越来越多——然而，美联储却在降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-12-18/financial-conditions-aren-t-tight-but-the-fed-is-still-cutting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储官员暗示 2025 年降息次数减少，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/treasuries-slide-as-fed-officials-signal-fewer-2025-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员根据最新的季度预测预计美联储 2025 年将减少降息次数，美国国债收益率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/treasuries-slide-as-fed-officials-signal-fewer-2025-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:19:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储暗示将减少宽松政策 黄金跌至一个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/gold-xauusd-holds-before-expected-us-rate-cut-as-traders-weigh-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储降息并预测2025年货币宽松力度减弱后，金价跌至一个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/gold-xauusd-holds-before-expected-us-rate-cut-as-traders-weigh-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:38:10 GMT</pubDate>
